title: Toy Soldier & Model Figure - May 2016
description:
English | 76 pages | PDF | 28 MB

Toy Soldier & Model Figure magazine is the world's number one magazine for collectors of all stripes. A colorful monthly publication bursting full of events, news, the latest ranges and kits available as well as historical facts to help fuel your passion! Whether you are a budding collector, or full-on aficionado, Toy Soldier is the ideal companion to your special hobby
